        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1345569049" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4949667779983232598">I chose this book on a whim, but I was very pleasantly surprised. Writing about mental illness can be a real challenge, after all if it was so easy to describe and convey to others it would be much less of a burden to bear. The book is simply written but very authentic in the way it describes mental illness from the inside out. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


